{"tid":1611891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"散仔協會又出來9up","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:56:29.000Z","uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e9454d8b6d0b660acaa82ef56bbed02b4f790f5e","tid":1611891,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=364795&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364795%26refer%3D&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=bd673d17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364795%26refer%3D&h=2ffc1a31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=364795&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】警隊員佐級協會發表聲明，指行政長官根據公安條例發出宵禁令，可以加強警隊止暴制亂的力度。<br />\n<br />\n協會主席林志偉在聲明中指，在反修例風波所衍生的社會衝突中，警隊一直孤身作戰。<br />\n<br />\n他說警方在形同戰場的暴動現場執勤，但政府到目前為止並沒有提出確實的針對措施，認為行政長官可以根據公安條例發出宵禁令，或者按緊急法採取針對性措施，將很大程度上加強警隊止暴制亂的效度及力度。他認為沒有適當的措施配合，警隊只是孤掌難鳴。"},{"pid":"48bc515ece563bc9982ae464d0bbec7d29a32134","tid":1611891,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"林大總統又出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201e08bf4ec4efdcef751282bd05e8016d0248fe","tid":1611891,"uid":15905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"一齊攬炒囉驚閪啊"},{"pid":"dfdd2e7606ee3a5129a4f65bfa909216d71a7e38","tid":1611891,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家指揮埋行政長官做嘢"},{"pid":"e776a7e4af63d9438fa6df9c3ae115c12ea81d4a","tid":1611891,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"而家香港係一個誰大誰惡誰正確既時代<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610696\" data